Class Pet

java.lang.Object
store.server.Animal
store.server.Pet
All Implemented Interfaces:
Cloneable, Animal_Preferences, Description
public class Pet extends Animal implements Description, Cloneable
Represents a Pet in the store. Extends the Animal class and implements the interface Description and Cloneable.
Author:
Rohit Verma
